high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter on the right side.
Pick up the potato to the left of the soap bottle on the counter.
Turn left and walk to the black fridge on the right.
Put the potato inside the fridge on the middle shelf to the right of the egg, chill it for seven seconds, remove it and close the doors.
Turn right and walk to the counter next to the fridge on your left.
Put the chilled potato to the left of the soap bottle on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled potato on a counter.

high_descs: Turn around and walk through the kitchen, turn to your right just past the sink and go to the counter between the refrigerator and the stove.
Pick up the potato, between the egg and the spoon, on the counter.
Go to the refrigerator to your left.
Place the potato in the refrigerator, on the second shelf, to the right of the egg, wait a moment for the potato to get cold, then remove the potato from the refrigerator.
Turn to your right and go back to the counter between the refrigerator and the stove.
Place the potato on the counter, to the left of the pump bottle.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold potato on the kitchen counter.

high_descs: Turn around and veer right to the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the potato on the counter.
Walk a step left to face the fridge.
Place the potato in the fridge to the right of the egg. Close the door, wait a moment, and then take it out.
Take a step right back to the counter.
Place the potato on the counter to the left of the soap bottle.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled potato on a counter.
